file.name: openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Livestorm - Public API
  description: |
    This is a generated connector for [Livestorm API v1](https://developers.livestorm.co/docs) OpenAPI specification.
    Client endpoint for Livestorm Public API.
    Livestorm is a browser based online web conferencing software used to share real-time live streams. 
    It can be used to power remote live meetings, product demos, sales webinars, online lessons, onboarding sessions, more.
    In addition, all request and response bodies, including errors, are encoded in JSON format.
  x-ballerina-init-description: >
    The connector initialization requires setting the API credentials. 

    Create an [Livestorm Account](https://app.livestorm.co/#/signup) and obtain tokens following [this guide](https://support.livestorm.co/category/4-getting-started).
  termsOfService: https://livestorm.co/terms/
  contact:
    name: Contact
    url: https://support.livestorm.co
    email: help@livestorm.co
  version: '1'
  x-ballerina-display:
    label: Livestorm
    iconPath: "icon.png"
servers:
- url: https://{defaultHost}
  variables:
    defaultHost:
      default: api.livestorm.co/v1
components:
  securitySchemes:
    api_key:
      description: All requests on the Livestorm API needs to include an API key. The API key can be provided as part of the query string or as a request header. The name of the API key needs to be `Authorization`.
      type: apiKey
      name: Authorization
      in: header
  schemas:
    Event:
      type: object
      description: Event response
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          description: Event ID
        type:
          type: string
          description: Event type
        attributes:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EventAttribute"
    Owner:
      type: object
      description: Owner details
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          description: Owner ID
        type:
          type: string
          description: Type
        attributes:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OwnerAttribute"
    Meta:
      type: object
      description: Metadata
      properties:
        record_count:
          type: integer
          description: Total record count
        page_count:
          type: integer
          description: Page count
        items_per_page:
          type: integer
          description: Items per page
    EventData:
      type: object
      description: Event post data
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          default: events
          description: Event type
          example: events
        attributes:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EventRequestAttribute"
        relationships:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EventRelationship"
    SessionData:
      type: object
      description: Add Session data
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          default: sessions
          description: Event type
          example: sessions
        attributes:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SessionRequestAttribute"
        relationships:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SessionRelationship"
    PeopleData:
      type: object
      description: Add People data
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          default: people
          description: Event type
          example: people
        attributes:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PeopleRequestAttribute"
    EventRequestAttribute:
      type: object
      description: Event request attributes
      properties:
        copy_from_event_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Event ID to copy
          example: 356b514f-333e-47d5-b5f2-3a4278b14072
        owner_id:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Owner ID
          example: f035b51d-5135-47ee-b1fc-4e92508f312a
        title:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Event title
          example: New event
        slug:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Event slug
          example: my-awesome-slug
    SessionRequestAttribute:
      type: object
      description: Session request attributes
      properties:
        estimated_started_at:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Estimated started time
        timezone:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Time zone
    PeopleRequestAttribute:
      type: object
      description: People request attributes
      properties:
        referrer:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Referrer detail
        utm_source:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: UTM tracking source
        utm_medium:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: UTM medium
        utm_term:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: UTM term
        utm_content:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: UTM content
        utm_campaign:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: UTM campaign
    OwnerAttribute:
      type: object
      description: Owner attributes
      properties:
        role:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Role of owner
        created_at:
          type: integer
          nullable: false
          description: Created timestamp
        updated_at:
          type: integer
          nullable: false
          description: Updated timestamp
        timezone:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Timezone
        first_name:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: First name
        last_name:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Last name
        email:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Email
        avatar_link:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Avatar link
    EventAttribute:
      type: object
      description: Event attributes
      properties:
        title:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Event title
          example: New event
        slug:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Event slug
          example: my-awesome-slug
        registration_link:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Event title
          example: https://app.livestorm.co/p/4d584b01-6319-4d19-a420-c67156273b76
        estimated_duration:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: Estimated duration
          example: 20      
        registration_page_enabled:
          type: boolean
          nullable: true
          description: Registration page enabled or not
          example: true
        everyone_can_speak:
          type: boolean
          nullable: true
          description: Everyone can speack or not
          example: true    
        description:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Description about event
          example: It is a webinar
        language:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Event language
          example: en      
        published_at:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: Updated timestamp
          example: 1625606595
        created_at:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: Created timestamp
          example: 1625606595  
        updated_at:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: Updated timestamp
          example: 1625606595       
        owner:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Owner"
        sessions_count:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: Number of sessions
          example: 1  
        fields:
          type: array
          items:
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Field"
          nullable: true
          description: Fields available
    Field:
      type: object
      description: Event fields
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Event field ID
          example: email  
        type:
          type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Type of fields
          example: text  
        order:
          type: integer
          nullable: true
          description: Order of fields
          example: 1  
        required:
          type: boolean
          nullable: true
          description: Required or not
          example: true  
    EventRelationship:
      type: object
      description: Event releationship
      properties:
        sessions:
          type: array
          items:
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Session"
          nullable: true
          description: Event session
    SessionRelationship:
      type: object
      description: Session releationship
      properties:
        people:
          type: array
          items:
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/People"
          nullable: true
          description: People
    Session:
      type: object
      description: Event session
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Session type
        id:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: Session ID
        attributes:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SessionAttribute"
    SessionAttribute:
      type: object
      description: Event session attribute
      properties:
        event_type_id:
          type: string
          description: Event type ID
        status:
          type: string
          description: Session status
        timezone:
          type: string
          description: Time zone
        room_link:
          type: string
          description: Url link to room
        attendees_count:
          type: string
          description: Number of Attendees
        duration:
          type: string
          description: Session duration
        estimated_started_at:
          type: string
          description: Estimated started time
        started_at:
          type: string
          description: Started time
        ended_at:
          type: string
          description: Ended time
        canceled_at:
          type: string
          description: Canceled time
        created_at:
          type: integer
          description: Created time
        updated_at:
          type: integer
          description: Updated time
        registrants_count:
          type: string
          description: Number of registrants
    People:
      type: object
      description: Event session
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: People type
        id:
          type: string
          nullable: false
          description: People ID
        attributes:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PeopleAttribute"
    PeopleAttribute:
      type: object
      description: People attribute
      properties:
        role:
          type: string
          description: Role assigned to
        created_at:
          type: integer
          description: Created time
        updated_at:
          type: integer
          description: Updated time
        timezone:
          type: string
          description: Time zone
        first_name:
          type: string
          description: First name
        last_name:
          type: string
          description: Last name
        email:
          type: string
          description: Email address
        avatar_link:
          type: string
          description: Avatar url link
tags:
- name: Events
  description: Webinars and Scheduled Meeting
- name: Sessions
  description: Webinar Session and Meeting
- name: People
  description: Participant and Team Member
paths:
  "/events":
    get:
      summary: List Events
      tags:
      - Events
      description: List all your organization's events.
      operationId: "listEvents"
      security:
      - api_key: []
      x-ballerina-display:
        label: Get List Of Events
      parameters:
      - name: pageNumber
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Page index to be returned
        required: false
        x-ballerina-display:
          label: Page Number
      - name: pageSize
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Number of record to be returned by page
        required: false
        x-ballerina-display:
          label: Page Size
      - name: filterTitle
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Filter events by title
        required: false
        x-ballerina-display:
          label: Title Filter
      - name: filterEveryoneCanSpeak
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Filter events by everyone can speak
        required: false
        x-ballerina-display:
          label: Filter By Everyone Can Speak Or Not
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Fetch List
          content:
            application/vnd.api+json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  data:
                    type: array
                    description: Event Data
                    items:
                      $ref: '#/components/schemas/Event'
                  meta:
                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Meta"
                required:
                - data
              examples:
                application/vnd.api+json:
                  value:
                    data:
                    - id: 30e06351-55b1-4908-8480-a9a7723eebcb
                      type: events
                      attributes:
                        title: loggins1
                        slug: tempore-quisquam
                        registration_link: https://app.livestorm.co/p/30e06351-55b1-4908-8480-a9a7723eebcb
                        estimated_duration: 30
                        registration_page_enabled: true
                        everyone_can_speak: false
                        description: Quia ullam est. Explicabo cumque laboriosam.
                          Eligendi earum delectus.1
                        language: en
                        published_at: 0
                        created_at: 1633046400
                        updated_at: 1633046400
                        owner:
                          id: 58bfd6bb-c5a2-4a90-8d78-42b9ab7f9439
                          type: people
                          attributes:
                            role: team_member
                            created_at: 1620049466
                            updated_at: 1620049466
                            timezone: Europe/Paris
                            first_name: Rhonda-4
                            last_name: Pataki-4
                            email: 4-ellie@ritchiesenger.io
                            avatar_link: 
                        sessions_count: 1
                        fields:
                        - id: email
                          type: text
                          order: 0
                          required: true
                        - id: first_name
                          type: text
                          order: 1
                          required: true
                        - id: last_name
                          type: text
                          order: 2
                          required: true
                        - id: avatar
                          type: file
                          order: 3
                          required: false
                        - id: input_text
                          type: text
                          order: 4
                          custom: true
                          required: true
                        - id: select_radio
                          type: multiple
                          order: 5
                          custom: true
                          options:
                            items:
                            - value: Choice A
                            - value: Choice B
                            - value: Choice C
                            multiple_answers: false
                          required: true
                        - id: select_checkbox
                          type: multiple
                          order: 6
                          custom: true
                          options:
                            items:
                            - value: Choice A
                            - value: Choice B
                            - value: Choice C
                            multiple_answers: true
                          required: true
                    meta:
                      record_count: 1
                      page_count: 1
                      items_per_page: 1
          headers:
            RateLimit-Montly-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of requests remaining for the current month
            RateLimit-Montly-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current month
            RateLimit-Interval-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of requests remaining for the current rate limit
                window (1 second)
            RateLimit-Interval-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current period (1
                second)
        '401':
          description: Authentication failed
          content: {}
    post:
      summary: Create a new event
      tags:
      - Events
      description: Create a new Event.
      operationId: "createEvent"
      security:
      - api_key: []
      x-ballerina-display:
        label: Create Event
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Create event response
          content:
            application/vnd.api+json:
              schema:
                type: object
                description: Create new event response
                properties:
                  data:
                    description: Record to represent 'Event',
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Event'
                    required:
                    - data
        '400':
          description: Bad request
          content: {}
        '401':
          description: Authentication failed
          content: {}
        '422':
          description: Team member not found
          content: {}
        '429':
          description: Too Many Requests
          content: {}
          headers:
            RateLimit-Interval-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current period (1
                second)
            RateLimit-Interval-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of remaining requests for the current period
                (1 second)
            Retry-After:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of seconds you are required to wait before the
                next successful request
            RateLimit-Reset:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: A timestamp of when the limit will be reset
      requestBody:
        description: "Request payload to create event"
        content:
          application/vnd.api+json:
            schema:
              type: object
              description: PosteventsRequest
              properties:
                data:
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EventData"
  "/events/{id}":
    get:
      summary: Retrieve an Event
      tags:
      - Events
      description: Get the details of an Event.
      operationId: "getEventByID"
      security:
      - api_key: []
      x-ballerina-display:
        label: Get Event By Event ID
      parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Event ID
        required: true
        x-ballerina-display:
          label: Event ID
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Get detail
          content:
            application/vnd.api+json:
              schema:
                type: object
                description: Get an event by ID response
                properties:
                  data:
                    description: Record to represent 'Event',
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Event'
                    required:
                    - data
          headers:
            RateLimit-Montly-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of requests remaining for the current month
            RateLimit-Montly-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current month
            RateLimit-Interval-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of requests remaining for the current rate limit
                window (1 second)
            RateLimit-Interval-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current period (1
                second)
        '401':
          description: Authentication failed
          content: {}
        '404':
          description: Not found
          content: {}
        '429':
          description: Too Many Requests
          content: {}
          headers:
            RateLimit-Interval-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current period (1
                second)
            RateLimit-Interval-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of remaining requests for the current period
                (1 second)
            Retry-After:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of seconds you are required to wait before the
                next successful request
            RateLimit-Reset:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: A timestamp of when the limit will be reset
  "/events/{id}/sessions":
    get:
      summary: List Sessions for an Event
      tags:
      - Events
      description: List all the Sessions that belong to the given Event.
      operationId: "listSessionByEvent"
      security:
      - api_key: []
      parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Event ID
        required: true
      - name: pageNumber
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Page index to be returned
        required: false
      - name: pageSize
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Number of record to be returned by page
        required: false
      - name: filterStatus
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: 'Filter Sessions by status : ''upcoming'', ''live'', ''on_demand'',
          ''past'', ''past_not_started'', ''canceled'', ''draft'''
        required: false
      - name: filterDateFrom
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Filter Sessions which â€˜estimated_started_atâ€™ attribute starts
          from the given date (expressed as a Unix timestamp or an ISO 8601 date).
        required: false
      - name: filterDateTo
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Filter Sessions which â€˜estimated_started_atâ€™ attribute ends with
          the given date (expressed as a Unix timestamp or an ISO 8601 date).
        required: false
      - name: include
        in: query
        schema:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            enum:
            - event
            - people
        description: Include Related Data
        required: false
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Fetch List
          content:
            application/vnd.api+json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  data:
                    type: array
                    description: Data
                    items:
                      allOf:
                      - "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Event"
                      - type: object
                        properties:
                          attributes:
                            type: object
                            description: Attributes
                            properties:
                              event_type_id:
                                type: string
                                nullable: true
                                description: ''
                              status:
                                type: string
                                nullable: false
                                description: ''
                              timezone:
                                type: string
                                nullable: false
                                description: ''
                              room_link:
                                type: string
                                nullable: false
                                description: ''
                              attendees_count:
                                type: integer
                                nullable: false
                                description: ''
                              duration:
                                type: integer
                                nullable: true
                                description: ''
                              estimated_started_at:
                                type: integer
                                nullable: false
                                description: ''
                              started_at:
                                type: integer
                                nullable: true
                                description: ''
                              ended_at:
                                type: integer
                                nullable: true
                                description: ''
                              canceled_at:
                                type: integer
                                nullable: true
                                description: ''
                              created_at:

                                description: ''

                  meta:
                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Meta"
                required:
                - data
              examples:
                application/vnd.api+json:
                  value:
                    data:
                    - id: ad77dadf-af08-4c60-b4b4-4aee48bb0192
                      type: sessions
                      attributes:
                        event_id: a1448868-eebc-43e8-a9b6-4365d3c73982
                        status: draft
                        timezone: Europe/Paris
                        room_link: https://app.livestorm.co/p/a1448868-eebc-43e8-a9b6-4365d3c73982/live?s=ad77dadf-af08-4c60-b4b4-4aee48bb0192
                        attendees_count: 0

                        updated_at: 1617461103
                        registrants_count: 3
                    meta:
                      record_count: 1
                      page_count: 1
                      items_per_page: 1
          headers:
            RateLimit-Montly-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of requests remaining for the current month
            RateLimit-Montly-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current month
            RateLimit-Interval-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of requests remaining for the current rate limit
                window (1 second)
            RateLimit-Interval-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current period (1
                second)
        '401':
          description: Authentication failed
          content: {}
        '404':
          description: Event Not found
          content: {}
        '429':
          description: Too Many Requests
          content: {}
          headers:
            RateLimit-Interval-Limit:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of allowed requests for the current period (1
                second)
            RateLimit-Interval-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of remaining requests for the current period
                (1 second)
            Retry-After:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: The number of seconds you are required to wait before the
                next successful request
            RateLimit-Reset:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: A timestamp of when the limit will be reset
    post:
      summary: Create a new event session
      tags:
      - Events
      description: Create a new Event Session.
      operationId: "createEventSession"
      security:
      - api_key: []
      parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        schema:
          type: string
        description: Event ID
        required: true
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Create event session response
          content:
            application/vnd.api+json:
              schema:
                type: object

                        people:

                          - type: people
